Key steps: 1. Group the terms \(4 + 5 + 6\) and subtract them from the sum of \(1 + 2 + 3\): \[ 1 + 2 + 3 - (4 + 5 + 6) \] 2. Compute the sum of \(1 + 2 + 3\): \[ 1 + 2 + 3 = 6 \] 3.
